#: ../../efi.rst:41
msgid "In the screenshot above, there are three boot options:"
msgstr "Dalam tangkapan layar di bawah ini, ada tiga pilihan boot:"

#: ../../efi.rst:43
msgid "``ubuntu`` at ``0000``"
msgstr "``ubuntu`` pada ``0000``"

#: ../../efi.rst:44
msgid "``linuxmint`` at ``0001``"
