msgid "Pre-installing Linux Mint (OEM Installation)"
msgstr "Pra-pemasangan Linux Mint (Pemasangan OEM)"

#: ../../oem.rst:4
msgid ""
"In the ISO boot menu, ``OEM install`` is used to preinstall Linux Mint."
msgstr ""
"Pada menu boot ISO, ``pasang OEM`` digunakan untuk melakukan prapemasangan "
"Linux Mint."

#: ../../oem.rst:6
msgid "This option is useful to:"
msgstr "Pilihan ini berguna untuk:"

#: ../../oem.rst:8
msgid ""
"Manufacturers and resellers who want to install Linux Mint on computers they "
"sell to their customers."
msgstr ""
"Produsen dan pengecer yang ingin memasang Linux Mint pada komputer yang "
"mereka jual kepada pelanggan mereka."

#: ../../oem.rst:9
msgid "People who want to sell or give their computer to somebody else."
msgstr ""
"Orang yang ingin menjual atau memberikan komputer mereka kepada orang lain."

#: ../../oem.rst:11
msgid ""
"When you install Linux Mint in ``OEM`` mode, the operating system is "
"installed with a temporary user account and prepared for the computer's "
"future owner."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda memasang Linux Mint dalam mode ``OEM``, sistem operasi dipasang "
"dengan akun pengguna sementara dan disiapkan untuk pemilik komputer masa "
"depan."

#: ../../oem.rst:13
msgid "The user account is set up by the new owner."
msgstr "Akun pengguna diatur oleh pemilik baru."

#: ../../oem.rst:15
msgid "To perform an OEM installation follow the steps below:"
msgstr "Untuk melakukan instalasi OEM ikuti langkah-langkah di bawah ini:"

#: ../../oem.rst:17
msgid "Select ``OEM Install`` from the USB stick (or DVD) menu."
msgstr "Pilih ``OEM Install`` dari menu USB stick (atau DVD)."

#: ../../oem.rst:19
msgid "Launch the installer and follow the installation instructions."
msgstr "Luncurkan penginstal dan ikuti instruksi instalasi."

#: ../../oem.rst:23
msgid ""
"Change any system settings or install additional software if you want."
msgstr ""
"Ubah pengaturan sistem apa pun atau pasang perangkat lunak tambahan jika "
"Anda mau."

#: ../../oem.rst:25
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Prepare for shipping to end user`, enter the "
"password you chose during the installation, click :guilabel:`OK` and shut "
"down the computer."
msgstr ""
"Jika sudah siap, klik :guilabel:`Siapkan pengiriman ke pengguna akhir`, "
"masukkan kata sandi yang Anda pilih selama pemasangan, klik :guilabel:`OK` "
"dan matikan komputer."

#: ../../oem.rst:31
msgid ""
"When the new owner of the computer boots the computer the following screen "
"appears:"
msgstr ""
"Ketika pemilik baru komputer mem-boot komputer, layar berikut muncul:"

#: ../../oem.rst:37
msgid ""
"The new owner selects his or her username, password, keyboard layout, "
"language, timezone and all the details relevant to create his or her user "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Pemilik baru memilih nama pengguna, kata sandi, tata letak papan ketik, "
"bahasa, zona waktu, dan semua detail yang relevan untuk membuat akun "
"penggunanya."

