#: ../../partitioning.rst:14
msgid "Dedicated /home partition"
msgstr "Partisi khusus /home"

#: ../../partitioning.rst:16
msgid ""
"In Linux, the ``/home`` directory is used to store user data and preferences."
msgstr ""
"Di Linux, direktori ``/home`` digunakan untuk menyimpan data dan preferensi "
"pengguna."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:18
msgid ""
"This directory contains one subdirectoy for each user account. Say your "
"username is ``john``, your home directory is ``/home/john``, your downloads "
"are in ``/home/john/Downloads``, your documents in ``/home/john/Documents``, "
"your Firefox bookmarks somewhere in ``/home/john/.mozilla`` and so on..."
msgstr ""
"Direktori ini berisi satu subdirektori untuk setiap akun pengguna. Misalkan "
"nama pengguna Anda adalah ``john``, direktori home Anda adalah "
"``/home/john``, unduhan Anda ada di ``/home/john/Downloads``, dokumen Anda "
"ada di ``/home/john/Documents``, markah Firefox Anda di suatu tempat di "
"``/home/john/.mozilla`` dan seterusnya..."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:20
msgid ""
"By giving ``/home`` its own dedicated partition, you separate the user data "
"from the rest of the operating system."
msgstr ""
"Dengan memberikan ``/home`` partisi khusus, Anda memisahkan data pengguna "
"dari sistem operasi lainnya."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:22
msgid ""
"The advantage is that you can wipe the operating system and replace it "
"without affecting the user data."
msgstr ""
"Keuntungannya adalah Anda dapat menghapus sistem operasi dan menggantinya "
"tanpa memengaruhi data pengguna."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:24
msgid "When installing Linux Mint:"
msgstr "Ketika memasang Linux Mint:"

#: ../../partitioning.rst:26
msgid ""
"Assign the ``/`` mount point to the partition dedicated to the operating "
"system, and tell the installer to format it."
msgstr ""
"Tetapkan titik kait ``/`` ke partisi khusus untuk sistem operasi, dan beri "
"tahu pemasang untuk memformatnya."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:28
msgid ""
"Assign the ``/home`` mount point to the partition dedicated to the user "
"data, and if it contains user data already, make sure to tell the installer "
"**not to format it**."
msgstr ""
"Tetapkan titik pemasangan ``/home`` ke partisi khusus untuk data pengguna, "
"dan jika sudah berisi data pengguna, pastikan untuk memberi tahu pemasang "
"**untuk tidak memformatnya**."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:31
msgid ""
"This is not recommended for novice users. A misstep during the installation "
"could wipe all your data. Always make backups, make sure to select the right "
"partitions and to carefully review formatting options."
msgstr ""
"Ini tidak disarankan untuk pengguna pemula. Salah langkah selama pemasangan "
"dapat menghapus semua data Anda. Selalu buat cadangan, pastikan untuk "
"memilih partisi yang tepat dan tinjau opsi pemformatan dengan cermat."

#: ../../partitioning.rst:34
msgid ""
"A Linux Mint operating system takes about 15GB and grows as you install "
"additional software. If you can spare the size, give it 100GB. Keep most of "
"your free space for the home partition. User data (downloads, videos, "
"pictures) takes a lot more space."
msgstr ""
"Sistem operasi Linux Mint membutuhkan sekitar 15GB dan membesar saat Anda "
"memasang perangkat lunak tambahan. Jika Anda bisa menyisihkan ukurannya, "
"berikan 100GB. Pertahankan sebagian besar ruang kosong Anda untuk partisi "
"home. Data pengguna (unduhan, video, gambar) membutuhkan lebih banyak ruang."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:2
msgid "System snapshots"
msgstr "Snapshot sistem"

#: ../../timeshift.rst:4
msgid ""
"Before you start using your operating system, set up system snapshots. Then "
"if anything goes wrong, you can restore your system from an earlier backup."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum Anda mulai menggunakan sistem operasi Anda, siapkan snapshot sistem. "
"Kemudian jika ada yang salah, Anda dapat memulihkan sistem Anda dari "
"cadangan sebelumnya."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:6
msgid "Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Administration --> Timeshift`."
msgstr "Luncurkan :menuselection:`Menu --> Administrasi --> Timeshift`."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:8
msgid "Select ``RSYNC`` and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr "Pilih ``RSYNC`` dan klik :guilabel:`Lanjut`."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:13
msgid ""
"Select the device where you want system snapshots to be saved and click "
":guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Pilih perangkat tempat Anda ingin menyimpan snapshot sistem dan klik "
":guilabel:`Lanjut`."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:19
msgid ""
"The selected device is not formatted and no data is lost. System snapshots "
"are saved into a newly created ``timeshift`` directory on the root of the "
"selected device."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat yang dipilih tidak diformat dan tidak ada data yang hilang. "
"Snapshot sistem disimpan ke dalam direktori ``timeshift`` yang baru dibuat "
"di akar perangkat yang dipilih."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:21
msgid "Select when system snapshots are saved."
msgstr "Pilih kapan snapshot sistem disimpan."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:27
msgid ""
"System snapshots are incremental so although the first snapshot takes a "
"significant amount of spaces, new snapshots only take additional space for "
"files which have changed."
msgstr ""
"Snapshot sistem bersifat tambahan sehingga meskipun snapshot pertama "
"membutuhkan banyak ruang, snapshot baru hanya membutuhkan ruang tambahan "
"untuk berkas-berkas yang telah berubah."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:30
msgid ""
"``Boot`` snapshots are performed in the background and do not impact the "
"speed of the boot sequence."
msgstr ""
"Snapshot ``Boot`` dilakukan di latar belakang dan tidak memengaruhi "
"kecepatan urutan boot."

#: ../../timeshift.rst:32
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Finish`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Selesai`."

#: ../../verify.rst:2
msgid "Verify your ISO image"
msgstr "Verifikasi image ISO Anda"

#: ../../verify.rst:4
msgid ""
"It is important to verify the integrity and authenticity of your ISO image."
msgstr "Penting untuk memverifikasi integritas dan keaslian image ISO Anda."

#: ../../verify.rst:6
msgid ""
"The integrity check confirms that your ISO image was properly downloaded and "
"that your local file is an exact copy of the file present on the download "
"servers. An error during the download could result in a corrupted file and "
"trigger random issues during the installation."
msgstr ""
"Pemeriksaan integritas mengonfirmasi bahwa image ISO Anda diunduh dengan "
"benar dan bahwa berkas lokal Anda adalah salinan persis dari berkas yang ada "
"di server unduhan. Kesalahan selama pengunduhan dapat menyebabkan berkas "
"rusak dan memicu masalah acak selama penginstalan."

#: ../../verify.rst:8
msgid ""
"The authenticity check confirms that the ISO image you downloaded was signed "
"by Linux Mint, and thus that it isn't a modified or malicious copy made by "
"somebody else."
msgstr ""
"Pemeriksaan keaslian mengonfirmasi bahwa image ISO yang Anda unduh "
"ditandatangani oleh Linux Mint, dan dengan demikian itu bukan salinan yang "
"dimodifikasi atau berbahaya yang dibuat oleh orang lain."

#: ../../verify.rst:11
msgid "Download the SHA256 sums provided by Linux Mint"
msgstr "Unduh SHA256 sum yang disediakan oleh Linux Mint"

#: ../../verify.rst:13
msgid ""
"All `download mirrors <https://www.linuxmint.com/mirrors.php>`_ provide the "
"ISO images, a ``sha256sum.txt`` file and a ``sha256sum.txt.gpg`` file. You "
"should be able to find these files in the same place you downloaded the ISO "
"image from."
msgstr ""
"Semua `cermin unduhan <https://www.linuxmint.com/mirrors.php>`_ menyediakan "
"image ISO, berkas ``sha256sum.txt``, dan berkas ``sha256sum.txt.gpg``. Anda "
"harus dapat menemukan berkas-berkas ini di tempat yang sama dengan tempat "
"Anda mengunduh image ISO."

#: ../../verify.rst:15
msgid ""
"If you can't find them, browse the `Heanet download mirror "
"<https://ftp.heanet.ie/mirrors/linuxmint.com/stable/>`_ and click the "
"version of the Linux Mint release you downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak dapat menemukannya, telusuri `Unduhan cermin Heanet "
"<https://ftp.heanet.ie/mirrors/linuxmint.com/stable/>`_ dan klik versi rilis "
"Linux Mint yang Anda unduh."

#: ../../verify.rst:17
msgid "Download both ``sha256sum.txt`` and ``sha256sum.txt.gpg``."
msgstr "Unduh ``sha256sum.txt`` dan ``sha256sum.txt.gpg``."

#: ../../verify.rst:19
msgid ""
"Do not copy their content, use \"right-click->Save Link As...\" to download "
"the files themselves and do not modify them in any way."
msgstr ""
"Jangan menyalin kontennya, gunakan \"klik kanan->Simpan Tautan Sebagai...\" "
"untuk mengunduh berkas itu sendiri dan jangan memodifikasinya dengan cara "
"apa pun."

#: ../../verify.rst:22
msgid "Integrity check"
msgstr "Pemeriksaan integritas"

#: ../../verify.rst:24
msgid ""
"To check the integrity of your local ISO file, generate its SHA256 sum and "
"compare it with the sum present in ``sha256sum.txt``."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memeriksa integritas berkas ISO lokal Anda, buat jumlah SHA256 dan "
"bandingkan dengan jumlah yang ada di ``sha256sum.txt``."

#: ../../verify.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you are using Windows follow the tutorial `How to verify the ISO image on "
"Windows <https://forums.linuxmint.com/viewtopic.php?f=42&t=291093>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menggunakan Windows, ikuti tutorial `Cara memverifikasi image ISO "
"di Windows <https://forums.linuxmint.com/viewtopic.php?f=42&t=291093>`_."

#: ../../verify.rst:33
msgid ""
"If the sums match, your ISO image was successfully downloaded. If they "
"don't, download it again."
msgstr ""
"Jika jumlahnya cocok, image ISO Anda berhasil diunduh. Jika tidak, unduh "
"lagi."

